features: 【Package Includes】: 32 pcs vintage paper with 16 pcs envelopes. The letter paper come in 2 different pattern designs, each with unique borders that are beautiful and elegant; The pattern on each envelope is different, with a strong retro vibe that can evoke your fond memories.

【High Quality Paper】: The parchment paper for writing is made of high quality paper, thick and durable, not easily damaged or faded, smooth surface, smooth writing, and can withstand a variety of writing tools without bleeding ink.

【Unique Design】: The airmail vintage envelopes are printed with vintage element patternss, which looks old and artistic. The color is elegant and generous, which can add a sense of fashion and retro to your writing.

【Size】: Lined Stationary Writing Paper: 9.3" X 6.9", envelope:6.9" X 4.9". The front of the paper is printed with lines, which can keep writing neat. The antique paper can make you rediscover the joy of pen and paper.

【Multiple Uses】: The stationery paper and envelopes set is suitable for many occasions, such as writing letters, making invitation cards, DIY craft projects, party invitations, etc. The old looking papers are an ideal gift for friends, family, colleagues, or anyone who loves writing letters.
